    <HediffDef>
    <defName>TW_Capacitor_Meltdown</defName>
    <label>电容紊乱</label>
	<defaultLabelColor>(0.8, 0.2, 0.2)</defaultLabelColor>
	<description>在电容过载爆炸后，特斯拉蜈蚣会陷入短暂的机能崩溃状态。高压电弧变得紊乱，移动速度大幅下降，攻击时甚至会出现短暂的电力中断。虽然它能通过自主充能逐渐恢复，但在完全回充前，无论是追击敌人还是防御反击都显得力不从心。</description>
    <hediffClass>HediffWithComps</hediffClass>
    <comps>
	  <li Class="HediffCompProperties_Disappears">
        <disappearsAfterTicks>3600</disappearsAfterTicks>
		<showRemainingTime>true</showRemainingTime>
      </li>
	  <li Class="NCL.HediffCompProperties_EffectAura">
        <minDistance>1.0</minDistance>  <!-- 最小5格距离 -->
        <maxDistance>3.0</maxDistance>  <!-- 最大6格距离 -->
        <EffectInterval>300</EffectInterval> <!-- 每2秒生成一轮 -->
        <EffectsPerBurst>1</EffectsPerBurst> <!-- 每次生成3个烟雾点 -->
		<EffectFleckDef>NCL_EnergyCrackle</EffectFleckDef>
      </li>
	</comps>
	<stages>
      <li>
		<minSeverity>0.01</minSeverity>
		<statFactors>
			<IncomingDamageFactor>2</IncomingDamageFactor><!--受到伤害乘数-->
			<StaggerDurationFactor>3</StaggerDurationFactor><!--抑止时间系数-->
			<MeleeDamageFactor>0.5</MeleeDamageFactor>
			<MoveSpeed>0.5</MoveSpeed>
        </statFactors>
		<statOffsets>
        </statOffsets>
      </li>
    </stages>
  </HediffDef>

    <HediffDef>
    <defName>NCL_Mech_ArchotechWorm_Hediff</defName>
    <label>NCL：超凡机械蠕虫</label>
	<defaultLabelColor>(0.8, 0.2, 0.2)</defaultLabelColor>
	<description>这个庞大机械体的身世被NCL封存在最高机密中，您虽充满好奇却无从探查。您亲眼见证过它在战场上展现的神迹般的杀伤效率，此刻只能庆幸它暂时属于同盟阵营——尽管这种特殊状态充满未知变数。</description>
    <hediffClass>HediffWithComps</hediffClass>
    <isBad>false</isBad>
    <comps>
	  <li Class="NCL.HediffCompProperties_MechAutoRecovery">
        <tickMultiflier>180</tickMultiflier>
        <healPoint>1</healPoint>
      </li>
	</comps>
	<stages>
      <li>
		<minSeverity>0.01</minSeverity>
		<statFactors>
			<StaggerDurationFactor>0</StaggerDurationFactor><!--抑止时间系数-->
        </statFactors>
		<statOffsets>
		  <MeleeHitChance>+10</MeleeHitChance>
		  <MeleeDodgeChance>+10</MeleeDodgeChance>
        </statOffsets>
      </li>
    </stages>
    <modExtensions>
        <li Class="NCL.HediffExtension_NoNotification"/>
    </modExtensions>
  </HediffDef>

