      <HediffDef>
    <defName>TW_Mech_Apocriton_Hediff</defName>
    <label>全面战争：憎恶毒蜂</label>
	<defaultLabelColor>(0.8, 0.2, 0.2)</defaultLabelColor>
	<description>憎恶毒蜂专有的光学迷彩模块，使其从战场上隐身。仅当玩家单位处于其附近25格范围内时隐身才会解除，在此之前该单位不进行攻击。</description>
    <hediffClass>HediffWithComps</hediffClass>
    <isBad>false</isBad>
    <comps>
        <li Class="NCL.HediffCompProperties_InvisibilityWithEnemyAwareness">
        <detectionRadius>25</detectionRadius> <!-- 检测半径 -->
        <checkInterval>60</checkInterval>
        <visibleToPlayer>true</visibleToPlayer>
	    </li>
        <li Class="HediffCompProperties_DisappearsOnDeath"/>
	</comps>
	<stages>
  </stages>
    <modExtensions>
        <li Class="NCL.HediffExtension_NoNotification"/>
    </modExtensions>
  </HediffDef>

